{"tid":2414901,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"蝗世宅吹雞起一個人漫畫底,又想去滋擾人","createTime":"2021-02-19T19:09:35.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-21T23:00:41.000Z","uid":26770,"like":30,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"243ee483a85d00133e2bf84d779e40f4c43cb024","tid":2414901,"uid":26770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T19:09:35.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hFJWgunoQas\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhFJWgunoQas&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGpKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=c5650875\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hFJWgunoQas</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/dokul1988/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fdokul1988%2F&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGpKGII16X6EVRppoT8yKAsg%3D&h=0d01c70d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/dokul1988/</a><br />\n<br />\n一個人漫畫因為屌蝗世宅屈椰子所以遭受批鬥<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cXzYVi3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcXzYVi3.png&h=0910ed72&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<ins>仲屈9我踢爆條友比幾百做保守黨會員扮政要係689指示</ins>"},{"pid":"01b076b9dafe2652a7c6f3e36a8d56e12d5d3d49","tid":2414901,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T19:11:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8ffbd8ba30b0cc1fb6d7051b317661d04989a95","tid":2414901,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T19:11:42.000Z","msg":"其實唔使理條傻㞗柒啦<br />\n由佢吠多兩句冇人和應就自然收皮"},{"pid":"42426de82b199b1e47fd077941cf326d2ca63d41","tid":2414901,"uid":26770,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"e8ffbd8ba30b0cc1fb6d7051b317661d04989a95","tid":2414901,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T19:11:42.000Z","msg":"其實唔使理條傻㞗柒啦<br />\n由佢吠多兩句冇人和應就自然收皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T19:15:10.000Z","msg":"國安良同蝗世宅個台就算訂閱有會員重疊<ins>都有幾萬人</ins><br />\n而呢班大把係<strong>退休去英美加澳又埋唔到堆的香港老野</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就係呢班無聊人日日捉鬼屈毛打發時間<br />\n大把手足比黑警夾左都係因為呢班捉鬼天師攪事"},{"pid":"051a96c32b52f9982a5950208b784b9e2d077202","tid":2414901,"uid":88134,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"quote":{"pid":"e8ffbd8ba30b0cc1fb6d7051b317661d04989a95","tid":2414901,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T19:11:42.000Z","msg":"其實唔使理條傻㞗柒啦<br />\n由佢吠多兩句冇人和應就自然收皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T20:43:24.000Z","msg":"我都想好似你咁講<br />\n但係你望下撐lunch哥班人柒咗都唔肯認既就知無你講得咁簡單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n何況呢隻世柒又唔係好似david lunch咁揸白卡仲讀過下書，間唔中都會講返小小正常野<br />\n只要用1%事實去遮住99%9up/風向<br />\n就可以取得民眾信任<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係lunch哥都要用幾個月時間先可以令群眾睇清楚佢真面目<br />\n講咗捉鬼係無用，講咗捉鬼之人才是鬼講到口都臭<br />\n但係我地有垃場咩？我地有蘋果咩？我地連平衡輿論既能力都無，結果係64晚會去唔去係連拗都無得拗（好彩當晚有人嗌獨立逆騎劫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />），結果係講咁耐捉鬼無用只會幫咗對家，都係唔會有黃絲理你。其實黃乜野絲呀，根本大部份都黃版藍屍嚟，權威性人格，專門服從威權統治者既，搞乜春民主運動姐，新加坡模式先最啱佢地<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有時我覺得香港人最終被滅族都係應份，世界本來就係殘酷，物競天擇，適者生存，連睇咩人分析跟乜野風向先係正途既選擇都做唔到，咁都唔洗講咩抗爭點樣先會贏啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身呢班人就唔撚會同你一齊出去打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9f7cb5eef64bb02a6e27b1e2b616f45fd098e13","tid":2414901,"uid":343189,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"42426de82b199b1e47fd077941cf326d2ca63d41","tid":2414901,"uid":26770,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"e8ffbd8ba30b0cc1fb6d7051b317661d04989a95","tid":2414901,"uid":38904,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T19:11:42.000Z","msg":"其實唔使理條傻㞗柒啦<br />\n由佢吠多兩句冇人和應就自然收皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T19:15:10.000Z","msg":"國安良同蝗世宅個台就算訂閱有會員重疊<ins>都有幾萬人</ins><br />\n而呢班大把係<strong>退休去英美加澳又埋唔到堆的香港老野</strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n就係呢班無聊人日日捉鬼屈毛打發時間<br />\n大把手足比黑警夾左都係因為呢班捉鬼天師攪事"}